</廢止註記>
<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.Date issued: 25 December 2015
2. Article 8, 10, 14, 15, 19, 20, 22, 24, and 29 to 33 amended and Article 38-1 added per 11 August 2017 Order No. Financial-Supervisory-Securities-Trading-1060025990 of the Financial Supervisory Commission
